When My bard is in a group with a chanter  I tell em - the only way I'm mezzing or charming, is if the chanter starts yelling. <P>I've grouped (with MY chanter) with bards that charm. And wasted too much mana doing it. <P>I totally agree. And I would've done the exact same thing, except I would've came back and soaked up the exp : ) <P>Let the bard do your job, you just sit, whip out your wand of allure and play chopstix  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"> <P>Muhahahhahaa
