This bard vs enchanter for crowd control discussion was fought on the bard board recently.  Can bards do effective crowd control? yes.  Should they do it when a good enchanter is in the group? no.<P>Can a good bard crowd control as well as a good enchanter? No.  How can you compare a bards 18 second mez to our 1.5 minute mez?  We're fire and forget and they constantly are retargetting and remezzing. Throw in our AE stuns and AE mezzes and there really is no comparison.  <P>Bards that insist on doing crowd control when there is a COMPETENT enchanter in the group are wasting their abilities.  Bards have many beneficial abilitites they can bring to a group, enchanters are specialists in only one area..crowd control.
</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="1"  face="Verdana, Arial">
